---

@type DeclKind
@kind sum
@purpose Discriminator for top-level declaration types. Used by DeclIndex to categorize declarations without needing to inspect the full AST node.
@variants
  DkFn — Function declaration (also used for extern fns and fixture blocks with name prefix "_extern"/"_fixture:")
  DkType — Type declaration (struct, sum type, newtype; also used for aliases with name prefix "_alias:")
  DkEnum — Enum declaration
  DkTrait — Trait declaration
  DkImpl — Impl block
  DkConst — Constant declaration
  DkEntry — Entry block (program main)
  DkTest — Test block (also used for bench blocks with name prefix "_bench:")
  DkUse — Use/import declaration
  DkNone — Sentinel
