@type BindingPower
@kind struct
@purpose Pratt parser binding power pair for infix operators. Left and right values determine associativity: left-associative has right=left+1, right-associative has right=left-1, non-associative has right=left.
@fields
  left: i64 — Left binding power (compared against min_bp to decide whether to consume this operator)
  right: i64 — Right binding power (passed as min_bp when parsing the right-hand operand)
