@fn new_pool
@sig () -> NodePool
@purpose Creates a new NodePool with a sentinel EkNone node at index 0. This sentinel ensures that index 0 always means "no node" and out-of-bounds lookups return a safe default.
@post Pool has exactly 1 node (the sentinel) at index 0
