@fn pool_add
@sig (pool: NodePool, e: Expr) -> NodePool
@purpose Appends a node to the pool and returns the updated pool. The new node's index is the previous pool_size().
@effects Allocates a new NodePool with the appended node (immutable append)
@post pool_size(result) == pool_size(pool) + 1
