@fn pool_get
@sig (pool: NodePool, idx: i64) -> Expr
@purpose Retrieves a node by index. Returns a sentinel EkNone if the index is out of bounds, providing safe default behavior instead of panicking.
@pre idx should be a valid pool index (0..pool_size-1) for meaningful results
@post Returns the sentinel _sentinel_expr() for out-of-bounds indices
